WEBVTT

00:05.539 --> 00:07.375
male announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:07.375 --> 00:11.145
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:11.145 --> 00:13.281
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:13.281 --> 00:15.116
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:15.116 --> 00:16.617
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:16.617 --> 00:18.719
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:18.719 --> 00:21.389
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:29.330 --> 00:32.166
- AH! IT HURTS, COACH.

00:32.166 --> 00:34.435
- IT'S JUST A CRAMP.

00:34.435 --> 00:36.604
HOLD IT, LET ME SEE.

00:36.604 --> 00:38.839
LET ME WORK ON IT.

00:38.839 --> 00:41.209
LOOSEN UP A LITTLE BIT,
COME ON.

00:41.209 --> 00:42.676
RELAX.

00:42.676 --> 00:44.212
YOU CAN'T PERFORM
WHEN YOU'RE TENSE.

00:44.212 --> 00:45.479
ALL RIGHT?

00:45.479 --> 00:48.316
LOOSEN UP A LITTLE BIT,
COME ON!

00:48.316 --> 00:49.550
[grunts]

00:49.550 --> 00:51.219
HEY!

00:51.219 --> 00:52.520
CAN'T THAT WAIT?

00:52.520 --> 00:56.557
- I'LL COME BACK.
- YEAH, DO THAT.

00:56.557 --> 00:58.092
ALL RIGHT? WE GOOD?

00:58.092 --> 01:00.328
THEN BACK TO WORK.
COME ON!

01:06.234 --> 01:09.337
[car alarm beeps]

01:09.337 --> 01:10.571
UNH!

01:10.571 --> 01:12.106
[screams]

01:12.106 --> 01:13.174
[stabbing]

01:13.174 --> 01:17.145
[screams]

01:17.145 --> 01:19.247
[moans]

01:19.247 --> 01:21.615
[whimpering]

01:26.187 --> 01:28.289
- WOW.

01:28.289 --> 01:29.623
WHOA.

01:29.623 --> 01:31.859
OLIVIA.

01:31.859 --> 01:34.428
[chuckles] IT'S A LITTLE EARLY
FOR VALENTINE'S DAY--

01:34.428 --> 01:36.697
- LOOK, HE AND I DECIDED
THAT WE WEREN'T QUITE READY

01:36.697 --> 01:38.732
FOR THE WHOLE VALENTINE'S DAY
DINNER THING, SO--

01:38.732 --> 01:41.435
- SO YOU WENT
FOR THE CASUAL PRE-DINNER THING.

01:41.435 --> 01:44.138
I GET THAT.
SORRY TO PULL YOU OUT.

01:44.138 --> 01:46.740
THIS IS ALEXEI BELYAKOV,

01:46.740 --> 01:48.709
BOY'S GYMNASTICS COACH.

01:48.709 --> 01:51.912
STABBED WITH AN ICE PICK.
HE BLED A LOT.

01:51.912 --> 01:53.581
LUCKY FOR THE VIC,
EMTs GOT HERE QUICK,

01:53.581 --> 01:54.915
OR WE'D BE CALLING WARNER.

01:54.915 --> 01:56.917
- AND THIS IS
OUR CASE BECAUSE...

01:56.917 --> 01:58.919
HE WAS STABBED
IN A BAD PLACE?

01:58.919 --> 02:01.755
- UH, BOTH OF THEM.

02:01.755 --> 02:04.858
- UH, ANY CHANCE THAT CSU
CAN GET PRINTS ON THE WEAPON?

02:04.858 --> 02:08.362
- THEY'LL HAVE TO WAIT TILL
THE COACH GETS OUT OF SURGERY.

02:12.333 --> 02:15.336
[dramatic music]

02:15.336 --> 02:23.411
*

02:59.380 --> 03:00.381
- DID YOU SEE
YOUR ATTACKER'S FACE?

03:00.381 --> 03:01.449
- NO.

03:01.449 --> 03:03.451
I WAS PUTTING MY BAG
IN THE TRUNK.

03:03.451 --> 03:06.454
HE CAME FROM BEHIND,
SLAMMED THE HOOD.

03:06.454 --> 03:08.289
- HE? YOU SURE
IT WAS A MAN?

03:08.289 --> 03:09.557
- I'M POSITIVE.

03:09.557 --> 03:11.925
HE HAD ON WORK GLOVES, BOOTS.

03:11.925 --> 03:14.362
SOME KIND OF OLIVE COVERALL.

03:14.362 --> 03:18.432
- AN ATTACK LIKE THIS,
UH, COULD BE REVENGE.

03:18.432 --> 03:20.701
- YEAH, MAYBE SOMETHING
IN YOUR PERSONAL LIFE?

03:20.701 --> 03:22.570
- I'M HAPPILY MARRIED.

03:22.570 --> 03:25.773
AND I'M ON GOOD RELATIONS
WITH ALL OF MY EX-WIVES.

03:25.773 --> 03:27.308
- WAIT. ALL?

03:27.308 --> 03:28.409
- THREE.

03:28.409 --> 03:30.278
I'M A ROMANTIC.

03:30.278 --> 03:33.314
- YOU EVER BEEN ROMANTIC
WITH SOMEONE YOU SHOULDN'T?

03:33.314 --> 03:35.549
- I LEARNED THAT LESSON
FOUR YEARS AGO.

03:35.549 --> 03:38.752
A STUDENT'S FATHER ACCUSED ME
OF BEING INVOLVED WITH HIS WIFE.

03:38.752 --> 03:41.589
- AND WERE YOU?

03:41.589 --> 03:43.757
DID HE ATTACK YOU?
- NO.

03:43.757 --> 03:45.593
HE TRIED TO RUIN ME.

03:45.593 --> 03:46.960
IN THE DIVORCE TRIAL,

03:46.960 --> 03:48.429
HE ACCUSED ME
OF MOLESTING HIS SON.

03:48.429 --> 03:50.498
AND SHE ACCUSED HIM.
[coughs]

03:50.498 --> 03:51.932
I WAS A PAWN.

03:51.932 --> 03:53.401
- ANY OTHER PARENTS
THREATEN YOU?

03:53.401 --> 03:56.337
- [sighs] A STUDENT
LAST YEAR. EDDIE.

03:56.337 --> 03:57.805
I HAD TO CUT HIM.

03:57.805 --> 04:00.774
I TOLD HIS MOTHER
I CAN'T SPIN STRAW INTO GOLD.

04:00.774 --> 04:02.009
- AND THE FATHER?

04:02.009 --> 04:05.379
- CAME IN,
THREW FURNITURE AROUND.

04:08.282 --> 04:10.651
- THESE RUSSIANS,
THEY'RE ALL LIARS.

04:10.651 --> 04:13.654
MAYBE--
MAYBE I KICKED A CHAIR.

04:13.654 --> 04:15.689
- YOU WERE MAD
'CAUSE ALEXEI CUT YOUR SON.

04:15.689 --> 04:17.325
- HE PLAYED US.

04:17.325 --> 04:18.659
AND WHEN
HE WANTED OUR MONEY,

04:18.659 --> 04:20.328
HE SAID EDDIE
HAD OLYMPIC POTENTIAL.

04:20.328 --> 04:22.830
THEN HE CHARGED US A FORTUNE
FOR PRIVATE LESSONS.

04:22.830 --> 04:25.466
- I DON'T WANT TO TALK
ABOUT COACH ALEXEI.

04:25.466 --> 04:27.601
- WELL, WHY NOT, EDDIE?

04:27.601 --> 04:29.770
'CAUSE HE CUT YOU?

04:29.770 --> 04:33.841
YOU KNOW, ALL THAT WORK,
PRIVATE SESSIONS.

04:33.841 --> 04:37.311
CAN YOU
TELL ME ABOUT THOSE?

04:37.311 --> 04:39.313
- HE WOULD PRACTICE WITH ME
ON THE BARS

04:39.313 --> 04:42.316
AND HELP ME
WITH MY STRETCHING.

04:42.316 --> 04:44.518
- STRETCHING.

04:44.518 --> 04:48.322
SO WHEN HE TOUCHED YOU,
DID THAT EVER MAKE YOU FEEL...

04:48.322 --> 04:49.690
UNCOMFORTABLE?

04:49.690 --> 04:53.427
- UH, WHAT, LIKE THAT?

04:53.427 --> 04:56.464
HE WASN'T THAT WAY.

04:56.464 --> 04:57.498
NOT WITH ME.

04:57.498 --> 05:00.568
- WAS HE THAT WAY
WITH OTHER KIDS?

05:00.568 --> 05:01.869
- I DON'T KNOW.

05:01.869 --> 05:05.439
HE HAD A LOT
OF PRIVATE SESSIONS.

05:05.439 --> 05:07.708
- COACH ALEXEI'S NOT GAY.
- MAYBE NOT.

05:07.708 --> 05:09.410
BUT HE'S PRETTY HANDS-ON.

05:09.410 --> 05:11.011
- YOU SAW THAT?
- I HEARD ABOUT IT.

05:11.011 --> 05:12.546
THIS GUY AT THE GYM,
WHEN EDDIE GOT CUT,

05:12.546 --> 05:15.383
SAID EDDIE WAS BETTER OFF
AWAY FROM THE COACH.

05:15.383 --> 05:17.084
- ANOTHER PARENT?
- NO, A YOUNG GUY.

05:17.084 --> 05:18.552
KIND OF LANKY.

05:18.552 --> 05:22.055
IN A JUMPSUIT.
PROBABLY WORKED MAINTENANCE.

05:22.055 --> 05:24.492
- JOHN DUBCEK.

05:24.492 --> 05:28.896
VANDALISM, POSSESSION,
DISORDERLY CONDUCT, BAR FIGHTS.

05:28.896 --> 05:33.033
BUT NOTHING
IN THE PAST FIVE YEARS.

05:33.033 --> 05:36.704
- STRAIGHTENED MYSELF OUT.
- TILL LAST NIGHT.

05:36.704 --> 05:39.440
ALEXEI ALMOST BLED OUT.
YOU COULD HAVE KILLED HIM.

05:39.440 --> 05:42.443
- UH, I DON'T KNOW
WHO YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

05:42.443 --> 05:44.077
- HOW LONG YOU BEEN WORKING
AT THAT GYM?

05:44.077 --> 05:45.679
YOU SEE HIM EVERY DAY.

05:45.679 --> 05:48.782
- I--
I SEE A LOT OF PEOPLE.

05:48.782 --> 05:51.485
- WE'RE GONNA FIND YOUR PRINTS
ON THAT WEAPON.

05:51.485 --> 05:52.853
- N-NO, YOU WON'T.

05:52.853 --> 05:55.122
- WHY, 'CAUSE YOU
WERE WEARING GLOVES?

05:55.122 --> 05:58.792
HIS BLOOD IS ON THEM.
ON YOUR BOOTS TOO.

05:58.792 --> 06:00.961
YOU KNOW,
AND I DON'T GET IT.

06:00.961 --> 06:05.065
YOUR BOSS, YOUR PAROLE OFFICER,
THEY VOUCH FOR YOU.

06:05.065 --> 06:08.602
- THIS COACH, WE HEARD
HE'S REAL ARROGANT, OKAY?

06:08.602 --> 06:10.971
SO WHAT DID HE DO TO YOU?
TREAT YOU BAD?

06:10.971 --> 06:12.673
BOTHER YOUR GIRLFRIEND
OR SOMETHING?

06:12.673 --> 06:15.008
- GIRLFRIEND?
I DON'T HAVE TIME.

06:15.008 --> 06:17.411
I WORK TWO JOBS,
AND I TAKE CARE OF MY MOM.

06:17.411 --> 06:20.080
- AND YOU LIVE
WITH YOUR MOM, RIGHT?

06:20.080 --> 06:22.683
YOUR BOSS TOLD US
THAT SHE WAS SICK.

06:22.683 --> 06:25.419
- SHE'S OKAY.
SHE'S NOT GONNA DIE.

06:25.419 --> 06:28.456
- YOU WANT TO BE THERE FOR HER?
YOU GOTTA HELP YOURSELF OUT.

06:28.456 --> 06:31.024
- COME ON, ALEXEI,
WHAT DID HE DO TO YOU?

06:31.024 --> 06:32.760
HE DISRESPECTED YOU,
HE YELLED AT YOU,

06:32.760 --> 06:34.595
HE'S COMPLAINING ABOUT YOU
TO HIS BOSS--

06:34.595 --> 06:35.929
- WHAT HE DOES,

06:35.929 --> 06:39.500
HE WOULDN'T TRY WITH ME.

06:39.500 --> 06:43.403
- WHAT HE DOES TO WHO,
JOHNNY?

06:47.908 --> 06:50.143
- THIS JANITOR
SAID I ABUSE MY STUDENT?

06:50.143 --> 06:51.912
HE'S PSYCHO.

06:51.912 --> 06:54.815
- JOHNNY DUBCEK SAYS
THAT HE SAW SOMETHING WRONG.

06:54.815 --> 06:56.216
WHY WOULD HE SAY THAT?

06:56.216 --> 06:58.652
- BECAUSE HE'S A JANITOR.
AN IDIOT!

06:58.652 --> 07:00.688
- SO YOU DON'T TAPE
YOUR SESSIONS?

07:00.688 --> 07:03.824
- OF COURSE I TAPE SESSIONS.
FOR THE BENEFIT OF THE STUDENT.

07:03.824 --> 07:06.660
A KID HAS A PROBLEM
WITH DISMOUNT? FILM IT.

07:06.660 --> 07:09.096
- OKAY, SO THIS RUBDOWN
THAT JOHNNY SAW YOU TAPING--

07:09.096 --> 07:10.764
WHO DOES THAT BENEFIT?

07:10.764 --> 07:12.900
- ME.
I STARTED FILMING EVERYTHING

07:12.900 --> 07:14.602
SINCE I WAS ACCUSED.

07:14.602 --> 07:17.605
TO SHOW I HAVE
NOTHING TO HIDE.

07:22.676 --> 07:24.177
- ANYBODY LEARN ANYTHING?

07:24.177 --> 07:27.515
- YEAH, 90 HOURS OF TAPE,
AND SO FAR HIS ONLY CRIME

07:27.515 --> 07:29.016
IS BORING ME TO DEATH.

07:29.016 --> 07:30.918
- LOOK, WE TALKED
TO A LOT OF HIS STUDENTS,

07:30.918 --> 07:32.152
BOTH FORMER AND CURRENT.

07:32.152 --> 07:33.587
I MEAN,
NOBODY LIKES THE GUY,

07:33.587 --> 07:35.155
BUT NOBODY
CALLED HIM A PREDATOR.

07:35.155 --> 07:39.192
- WELL, IT SOUNDS LIKE
WE OWE THE COACH AN APOLOGY.

07:39.192 --> 07:42.696
- CAPTAIN, DUBCEK BELIEVES
WHAT HE TOLD US.

07:42.696 --> 07:44.532
- LOOK, THE COACH DOES
PUT HIS HANDS ON THESE KIDS,

07:44.532 --> 07:46.667
AND MAYBE DUBCEK
MISCONSTRUED.

07:46.667 --> 07:48.536
- AND STABBED THE GUY
IN THE TESTICLES?

07:48.536 --> 07:50.103
SOMETHING SET HIM OFF.

07:50.103 --> 07:52.139
- WELL, HE'S GOT ONE LAST CHANCE
TO TELL US WHAT.

07:52.139 --> 07:55.042
HE'S BEEN ARRAIGNED.
HE'S ON HIS WAY TO RIKERS NOW.

08:02.149 --> 08:04.217
- PRISONER VAN HAS ARRIVED
AT THE FACILITY.

08:04.217 --> 08:08.021
SIX MALE PRISONERS.

08:15.262 --> 08:17.164
- [grunting]

08:17.164 --> 08:18.932
- HEY, I NEED HELP!
HE'S CHOKING HIM!

08:18.932 --> 08:20.067
- LET HIM GO!

08:20.067 --> 08:22.002
- PULL HIM OFF!
PULL HIM OFF!

08:22.002 --> 08:23.637
[indistinct chatter]

08:23.637 --> 08:24.738
- I GOT HIM.

08:24.738 --> 08:26.173
WATCH HIS HEAD.
WATCH HIS HEAD.

08:26.173 --> 08:27.575
PUT HIM ON THE DECK.

08:27.575 --> 08:30.811
- [panting]

08:34.848 --> 08:36.116
- IT'S NOT MY FAULT.

08:36.116 --> 08:37.685
I TOLD THEM NOT
TO PUT ME IN WITH THAT!

08:37.685 --> 08:39.152
- PUT HIM IN THE CAR.
- WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

08:39.152 --> 08:40.654
- DUBCEK WENT NUTS
ON THE TRUCK,

08:40.654 --> 08:42.255
TRIED TO KILL
THE INMATE NEXT TO HIM.

08:42.255 --> 08:44.291
- WHAT WAS HE SAYING,
"DON'T PUT ME IN WITH THAT"?

08:44.291 --> 08:46.126
- WHEN WE HAD HIM AT
THE COURTHOUSE LOADING HIM IN,

08:46.126 --> 08:47.127
HE SAID HE DIDN'T WANT TO BE
IN THE TRUCK WITH THIS PRISONER.

08:47.127 --> 08:48.696
- THE PRISONER THREATEN HIM?

08:48.696 --> 08:50.230
- NAH, SOME PEDOPHILE ARRAIGNED
FOR TOUCHING BOY SCOUTS.

08:50.230 --> 08:51.899
- PEDOPHILE?
- UH-HUH.

08:51.899 --> 08:54.034
- IS THERE ANY CHANCE
I CAN TALK TO JOHNNY?

08:54.034 --> 08:57.705
- NOT HERE.
TRY ARRAIGNMENT.

09:00.207 --> 09:03.611
- TWO VIOLENT ASSAULTS
IN THREE DAYS, MR. DUBCEK.

09:03.611 --> 09:04.712
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON WITH YOU,

09:04.712 --> 09:06.580
BUT I BETTER NOT
SEE YOU HERE AGAIN.

09:06.580 --> 09:08.682
THE DEFENDANT IS REMANDED
BACK TO RIKERS.

09:08.682 --> 09:09.917
[gavel thumps]

09:09.917 --> 09:13.721
- I'M SORRY, MOM.

09:13.721 --> 09:15.723
- WE'RE NOT GETTING
TO HIM FOR A WHILE.

09:15.723 --> 09:17.691
- YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
IN JOHNNY'S MIND,

09:17.691 --> 09:19.727
HE'S GONE OFF
ON TWO PEDOPHILES.

09:19.727 --> 09:23.030
THINK THE MOTHER
KNOWS WHY?

09:23.030 --> 09:24.164
- JOHNNY'S BEEN
CLEAN AND SOBER,

09:24.164 --> 09:26.366
NO TROUBLE, NO--
NO FIGHTS

09:26.366 --> 09:27.901
SINCE HE WAS A TEENAGER.

09:27.901 --> 09:30.170
- LOT OF BOYS GO THROUGH TROUBLE
DURING THAT TIME.

09:30.170 --> 09:32.139
- MM.
- WAS HIS FATHER AROUND MUCH?

09:32.139 --> 09:34.074
- NO, JOHNNY'S FATHER
DIED WHEN HE WAS TEN.

09:34.074 --> 09:37.711
- ANY OTHER MEN
IN JOHNNY'S LIFE AFTER THAT?

09:37.711 --> 09:39.212
- WELL, A FEW YEARS LATER,

09:39.212 --> 09:41.982
IN OUR NEIGHBORHOOD HOUSE,
CLINTON,

09:41.982 --> 09:44.685
THIS COACH
TOOK AN INTEREST

09:44.685 --> 09:46.687
IN JOHNNY.

09:46.687 --> 09:49.723
HE EVEN MANAGED TO GET JOHNNY
INTO THE OPEN AIR CAMP UPSTATE.

09:49.723 --> 09:51.625
- DID JOHNNY
LIKE IT UP THERE?

09:51.625 --> 09:54.161
- NOT SO MUCH.

09:54.161 --> 09:57.865
COACH SCHULTZ SAID THAT
JOHNNY WAS VERY HOMESICK.

09:57.865 --> 10:01.401
AND WHEN HE GOT HOME FROM CAMP,
HE JUST WASN'T THE SAME.

10:01.401 --> 10:05.706
I COULDN'T EVEN DRAG HIM
TO CLINTON HOUSE.

10:05.706 --> 10:07.407
- SO WE TALKED
TO JOHNNY DUBCEK.

10:07.407 --> 10:10.310
HE ADMITTED ALL HE SAW
WAS COACH ALEXEI

10:10.310 --> 10:11.845
HELPING A STUDENT STRETCH.

10:11.845 --> 10:14.047
- ALL RIGHT,
SO HE OVERREACTED.

10:14.047 --> 10:17.084
DOES JOHNNY HAVE A HISTORY
OF BEING ASSAULTED?

10:17.084 --> 10:20.087
- MOM SAYS SOMETHING WENT ON
ONE SUMMER WITH A CAMP COACH.

10:20.087 --> 10:21.889
- OKAY,
SO WE'VE SEEN THIS BEFORE.

10:21.889 --> 10:24.057
SOMEBODY
SUFFERS A SEXUAL ABUSE,

10:24.057 --> 10:27.094
THEN THEY MANAGE TO FUNCTION
UNTIL THERE'S A TRIGGER.

10:27.094 --> 10:29.429
HE SEES COACH ALEXEI
TOUCH A BOY,

10:29.429 --> 10:31.164
AND IT SETS HIM OFF.

10:31.164 --> 10:33.701
- THEN HE'S CHAINED
TO A PEDOPHILE?

10:33.701 --> 10:35.669
YOU WANT TO SET OFF
PTSD IN SOMEONE,

10:35.669 --> 10:37.705
COULDN'T HAVE
PLANNED IT BETTER.

10:37.705 --> 10:39.907
- WELL, THAT'S ALL SOMETHING
HIS DEFENSE CAN BRING UP,

10:39.907 --> 10:41.842
AND I'LL MAKE SURE THE D.A.
PASSES THAT ALONG.

10:41.842 --> 10:43.443
- HOLD ON.
THAT'S IT?

10:43.443 --> 10:47.347
WHAT ABOUT THIS CAMP COACH?
- IT'S MARTIN SCHULTZ.

10:47.347 --> 10:49.717
HE WORKED
IN A CLINTON NEIGHBORHOOD HOUSE.

10:49.717 --> 10:51.384
IN THE SUMMERS,
HE RAN OPEN AIR CAMP.

10:51.384 --> 10:54.121
HE TOOK INNER-CITY KIDS
UP TO THE ADIRONDACKS.

10:54.121 --> 10:57.925
- DID DUBCEK ACCUSE HIM,
OR IS ALL OF THIS INFERENCE?

10:57.925 --> 11:00.694
- DUBCEK WAS PRETTY SHUT DOWN.
- SO THAT'S A NO.

11:00.694 --> 11:02.830
AND IF SCHULTZ HAD A RECORD,
YOU WOULD HAVE TOLD ME.

11:02.830 --> 11:05.432
- LIKE FATHER GEOGHAN
OR SANDUSKY?

11:05.432 --> 11:06.800
YOU KNOW HOW IT GOES.

11:06.800 --> 11:08.435
EVEN WHEN PEOPLE
TRY TO COME FORWARD,

11:08.435 --> 11:09.970
IT ALWAYS GETS HUSHED UP.

11:09.970 --> 11:12.139
- OR IT'S ALL JUST
A MISUNDERSTANDING,

11:12.139 --> 11:13.406
LIKE COACH ALEXEI.

11:13.406 --> 11:15.308
- OKAY, THIS SCHULTZ--

11:15.308 --> 11:18.411
LET'S AT LEAST SEE
IF HE'S STILL WORKING WITH KIDS.

11:19.947 --> 11:22.115
WE WANTED TO ASK YOU
ABOUT ONE OF YOUR OLD KIDS,

11:22.115 --> 11:25.185
JOHNNY DUBCEK.
- DUBCEK?

11:25.185 --> 11:27.320
I'VE BEEN WORKING WITH KIDS
FOR 50 YEARS NOW.

11:27.320 --> 11:29.156
I DON'T KNOW,
I--WHEN WAS THIS?

11:29.156 --> 11:30.724
- IT WAS THE EARLY '90s.

11:30.724 --> 11:32.459
YEAH, HIS DAD DIED
WHEN HE WAS TEN.

11:32.459 --> 11:33.894
YOU KNEW HIM
FROM CLINTON HOUSE.

11:33.894 --> 11:36.063
HE HAS BLUE EYES,
LIGHT BROWN HAIR.

11:36.063 --> 11:38.265
- OH, JOHNNY,
BIG METS FAN.

11:38.265 --> 11:41.068
HE USED TO WEAR
THIS RATTY, ORANGE T-SHIRT

11:41.068 --> 11:42.369
EVERY DAY TO CAMP.

11:42.369 --> 11:44.071
EVERY SINGLE DAY.

11:44.071 --> 11:48.041
THE OTHER KIDS TEASED HIM
SOMETHING FIERCE.

11:48.041 --> 11:50.443
YOU'RE COPS.
- MM-HMM.

11:50.443 --> 11:53.981
- YEAH, HE DO SOMETHING WRONG?
- HE ASSAULTED A COUPLE OF MEN.

11:53.981 --> 11:56.817
HE'S GOING AWAY
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

11:56.817 --> 11:59.452
- ANYTHING I CAN DO?
- WELL, WE'RE NOT SURE.

11:59.452 --> 12:02.155
WE'RE TRYING TO UNDERSTAND
THE BOY WHO BECAME THE MAN.

12:02.155 --> 12:04.491
- OH, THAT'S ALWAYS
THE TOUGH ONE, ISN'T IT?

12:04.491 --> 12:07.160
HE COULD HAVE GONE
EITHER WAY.

12:07.160 --> 12:09.763
UH, THE KID HAD
A LOT OF POTENTIAL.

12:09.763 --> 12:10.998
- YEAH, HIS MOM
WAS TELLING US

12:10.998 --> 12:14.367
THAT HE WAS
A STRAIGHT-A STUDENT...

12:14.367 --> 12:15.803
TILL HE WENT TO CAMP HERE.

12:15.803 --> 12:19.406
- HEY, LISTEN,
