- AND YOU GOT ALL THIS
FROM A CUP OF HOT CHOCOLATE?

14:11.618 --> 14:14.187
- LOOK, EVERYTHING HE DOES
IS PREMEDITATED.

14:14.187 --> 14:15.655
EVERY WORD, EVERY LOOK.

14:15.655 --> 14:19.059
- SO YOU'RE TELLING ME
HE DIDN'T CONFESS?

14:19.059 --> 14:21.394
WELL, IF THIS GUY
HAS WORKED WITH KIDS

14:21.394 --> 14:24.164
FOR OVER 50 YEARS
AND THERE'S NOT ONE COMPLAINT--

14:24.164 --> 14:26.033
- BECAUSE HE KNOWS
WHO TO PICK.

14:26.033 --> 14:29.136
HE FINDS SINGLE MOTHERS
