SHAMED INTO SILENCE.

14:48.621 --> 14:51.491
SO WHATEVER SCHULTZ DID
TO THOSE MEN

14:51.491 --> 14:55.929
WHEN THEY WERE BOYS...

14:55.929 --> 15:00.233
