15:31.564 --> 15:34.601
- WE ONLY NEED ONE TO START.

15:34.601 --> 15:36.503
REGGIE RHODES, OKAY?

15:36.503 --> 15:38.238
AND HE'S NOT GONNA BE WORRIED
ABOUT BEING A TARGET

15:38.238 --> 15:41.241
BECAUSE HE'S ON DEATH ROW
