TO BE PUNISHED FOR WHAT HE DID,

16:13.073 --> 16:16.643
THEN WE NEED SOMEBODY
BRAVE ENOUGH TO COME FORWARD.

16:16.643 --> 16:18.678
- I CAN'T.

16:18.678 --> 16:20.480
I DON'T WANT
TO THINK ABOUT HIM.

16:20.480 --> 16:24.051
I DON'T WANT
TO THINK ABOUT ANY OF THEM.

16:24.051 --> 16:27.020
- THEM?
- THE MAN YOU MURDERED.

16:27.020 --> 16:30.123
AT TRIAL, THEY SAID
HE WAS A STRANGER.

16:30.123 --> 16:32.425
YOU WERE JUST ROBBING HIM
IN HIS HOUSE.

16:32.425 --> 16:37.230
IS THERE MORE
TO IT THAN THAT?

16:39.799 --> 16:43.603
- DOESN'T MATTER.
