TAKE THAT BACK.

16:47.074 --> 16:49.376
I'M TRYING TO STAY
AT PEACE.

16:49.376 --> 16:53.012
NOW GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE NOW!

17:04.324 --> 17:05.725
- SO HOW DOES THIS
CROSS YOUR DESK?

17:05.725 --> 17:07.827
- BECAUSE WE ARE TRACKING
A CAREER PEDOPHILE,

17:07.827 --> 17:10.597
MARTIN SCHULTZ,
AND WE BELIEVE THAT REGGIE

17:10.597 --> 17:13.300
IS ONE OF A DOZEN VICTIMS
WHO WENT ON

17:13.300 --> 17:15.468
TO COMMIT VIOLENT CRIMES
THEMSELVES.

17:15.468 --> 17:18.105
- SO ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT A DEATH PENALTY CASE HERE

17:18.105 --> 17:19.739
OR ME DOING SVU'S JOB?

17:19.739 --> 17:21.608
- A LITTLE OF BOTH.

17:21.608 --> 17:23.643
- SO YOU'RE ASKING ME
FOR A FAVOR.

17:23.643 --> 17:27.780
SO...YOU'RE NOT ANGRY
WITH ME ANYMORE?

17:29.249 --> 17:31.551
- I WAS NEVER ANGRY.
- NO?

17:31.551 --> 17:33.320
YOU HAD A RIGHT TO BE.

17:33.320 --> 17:37.524
I BLEW UP YOUR RELATIONSHIP
WITH DAVID HADEN.

17:37.524 --> 17:40.327
- OKAY, I WAS ANGRY.

17:40.327 --> 17:43.396
BUT I ALSO KNEW YOU THAT YOU
WERE DOING RIGHT BY YOUR CLIENT.

17:46.433 --> 17:50.370
BAYARD, JUST TAKE A LOOK
AT REGGIE'S CASE.

17:50.370 --> 17:51.771
OKAY?
THE D.A. SAID

17:51.771 --> 17:55.775
THAT THIS WAS A ROBBERY
GONE BAD, BUT NOTHING WAS TAKEN,

17:55.775 --> 17:59.546
AND THE MAN THAT HE MURDERED
HAD TWO PRIOR SOLICITATIONS

17:59.546 --> 18:03.650
FOR YOUNG BLACK MEN.

18:03.650 --> 18:08.355
- AND THIS NEVER
CAME OUT AT TRIAL?

18:08.355 --> 18:11.358
AND REGGIE NEVER REFERENCED
A SEXUAL RELATIONSHIP?

18:11.358 --> 18:15.562
- PROBABLY TOO ASHAMED
TO ADMIT IT.

18:16.896 --> 18:21.401
IF WE DON'T HELP HIM,
HE DIES IN NINE DAYS.

18:26.639 --> 18:28.408
- SO IF I TALK TO YOU,

18:28.408 --> 18:31.344
MR. ELLIS WILL HELP
WITH MY DEFENSE?

18:31.344 --> 18:33.446
- I READ THE TRANSCRIPT
OF YOUR TWO-DAY TRIAL.

18:33.446 --> 18:34.847
I'LL HELP EITHER WAY.

18:34.847 --> 18:38.318
- BUT MY LAST LAST ATTORNEY,
MR. AMIRI,

18:38.318 --> 18:39.919
HE SAID IT WAS TOO LATE.
- IT'S NOT.

18:39.919 --> 18:41.421
