IT'S STATE-SANCTIONED MURDER.

20:11.411 --> 20:13.480
YOU HAVE ANY VACATION DAYS
ACCUMULATED?

20:13.480 --> 20:16.416
- OH, I DON'T KNOW.
50, 60 WEEKS.

20:16.416 --> 20:17.917
- WELL, GOOD,
YOU'RE IN LUCK.

20:17.917 --> 20:20.487
CLEVELAND'S LOVELY
THIS TIME OF YEAR.

20:20.487 --> 20:22.689
AND I'M GOING
TO NEED YOUR HELP.

20:25.758 --> 20:27.627
- RHODES...

20:27.627 --> 20:29.529
REGGIE RHODES.

20:29.529 --> 20:30.830
- HE'S ONE
OF YOUR DEATH ROW CLIENTS.

20:30.830 --> 20:31.831
- FOUND GUILTY OF KILLING
CHARLES DANFORTH,

20:31.831 --> 20:33.533
FATHER OF THREE.

20:33.533 --> 20:35.502
