HE TOLD ME HE DID IT.

20:50.350 --> 20:51.984
- DID HE ALSO TELL YOU
THAT HE MET

20:51.984 --> 20:53.386
HIS ORIGINAL DEFENSE ATTORNEY
THE DAY BEFORE THE TRIAL

20:53.386 --> 20:55.388
