WAS SUBSEQUENTLY DISBARRED?

20:55.388 --> 20:58.658
- A DEFENDANT IS
ONLY ENTITLED TO COUNSEL,

20:58.658 --> 21:01.494
NOT QUALITY OF COUNSEL.

21:01.494 --> 21:04.364
- MR. AMIRI,
WE'VE ALSO BECOME AWARE

21:04.364 --> 21:06.533
THAT MR. RHODES
WAS A VICTIM

21:06.533 --> 21:08.568
OF SEXUAL ABUSE
AS A CHILD.

21:08.568 --> 21:10.370
