ABOUT MITIGATING CIRCUMSTANCES,

21:23.516 --> 21:24.817
PERIOD.

21:24.817 --> 21:27.787
- MR. ELLIS,
WHAT WE DO IS TRIAGE.

21:27.787 --> 21:29.889
I'VE GOT PEOPLE ON DEATH ROW
FOR CRIMES THEY DIDN'T COMMIT.

21:29.889 --> 21:32.392
YOU THINK YOU CAN COME IN
AND DO A BETTER JOB,

21:32.392 --> 21:33.693
HAVE AT IT.

21:33.693 --> 21:37.029
- THANK YOU.

21:37.029 --> 21:40.032
