I WANTED TO HEAR.

21:42.902 --> 21:44.571
REGGIE, WE NEED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED

21:44.571 --> 21:46.038
THAT NIGHT
AT CHARLES DANFORTH'S HOUSE.

21:46.038 --> 21:48.408
- I CAN'T GO BACK
TO THAT PLACE, MAN.

21:48.408 --> 21:50.810
- THE JURY WAS TOLD THAT YOU
HAD NEVER MET DANFORTH BEFORE.

21:50.810 --> 21:52.745
AND THAT NIGHT,

21:52.745 --> 21:55.482
