FOR AN ODD JOB?

21:55.482 --> 21:58.918
- REGGIE, WE KNOW
THAT HE HIRED OTHER YOUNG MEN,

21:58.918 --> 22:01.854
AND IT WASN'T
FOR ODD JOBS.

22:03.756 --> 22:07.560
