IN HIS HOME?

22:07.560 --> 22:10.096
- REGGIE, YOU'VE GOT
TO HELP YOURSELF HERE.

22:10.096 --> 22:12.899
- WHY ARE WE DOING THIS?
IT'S OVER.

22:12.899 --> 22:14.901
- THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN TELL THIS WOMAN

22:14.901 --> 22:17.036
THAT SHE HASN'T HEARD.

22:17.036 --> 22:19.439
THERE'S NOTHING YOU COULD SAY
THAT WOULD MAKE YOU

22:19.439 --> 22:23.643
