22:37.490 --> 22:41.494
- NO, THANK YOU, MA'AM.

22:41.494 --> 22:43.430
- REGGIE, YOU SAID BEFORE
THAT YOU DIDN'T WANT TO TALK

22:43.430 --> 22:44.831
ABOUT ANY OF THEM.

22:44.831 --> 22:47.967
MARTIN...

22:47.967 --> 22:52.171
HE WASN'T THE FIRST.

22:52.171 --> 22:55.708
HOW OLD WERE YOU
WHEN IT STARTED?

23:01.548 --> 23:05.485
- WELL, THE FIRST TIME
I CAN REMEMBER...

23:05.485 --> 23:09.388
FIVE, MAYBE SIX.

23:13.493 --> 23:15.562
SEE, MY UNCLE...

23:15.562 --> 23:19.566
