HIS MOTHER'S BOYFRIEND, OR PIMP.

23:35.482 --> 23:38.785
AND AT TEN,
IT WAS A TEACHER IN SCHOOL.

23:38.785 --> 23:40.853
I MEAN,
PREDATORS HAVE RADAR.

23:40.853 --> 23:42.589
- AND SCHULTZ?
- THREE SUMMERS.

23:42.589 --> 23:45.958
AND BY THE END, SCHULTZ WAS
PASSING HIM AROUND TO OTHER MEN.

23:45.958 --> 23:47.694
SO REGGIE DROPS
OUT OF SCHOOL,

23:47.694 --> 23:50.096
HE HITCHHIKES,
AND ENDS UP HERE IN CLEVELAND.

23:50.096 --> 23:52.699
