24:59.832 --> 25:01.601
- I PRAY FOR HIM
EVERY DAY.

25:01.601 --> 25:03.536
- 'CAUSE YOU KNOW
WHAT HE WENT THROUGH...

25:03.536 --> 25:07.306
THAT IT WAS MORE
THAN JUST YOUR UNCLE.

25:07.306 --> 25:09.275
- I KNOW.

25:09.275 --> 25:13.580
- KASSANDRA, YOU COULDN'T
PROTECT HIM GROWING UP.

25:13.580 --> 25:17.784
HELP HIM NOW.

25:17.784 --> 25:19.619
- REGGIE...
REGGIE RHODES?

25:19.619 --> 25:21.120
GOOD GOD ALMIGHTY.

25:21.120 --> 25:22.555
WHEN HE SHOWED UP
AT THIS CAMP,

25:22.555 --> 25:24.323
HE DIDN'T EVEN
HAVE A TOOTHBRUSH.

25:24.323 --> 25:26.225
A PAIR OF SHORTS,

25:26.225 --> 25:27.960
A PAIR OF OLD,
HIGH-TOP, DIRTY SNEAKERS.

25:27.960 --> 25:31.964
HIS MOTHER
WAS A CRACK ADDICT, OR WORSE.

25:31.964 --> 25:33.666
- ANYTHING ELSE
YOU REMEMBER ABOUT HIM?

25:33.666 --> 25:35.902
- A 12-YEAR-OLD KID
WITH A RAP SHEET

25:35.902 --> 25:37.236
AS LONG AS YOUR ARM.

25:37.236 --> 25:39.338
BUT UNDERNEATH,
HE'S A SWEET KID.

25:39.338 --> 25:41.007
SWEET KID.

25:41.007 --> 25:45.277
UNTIL HE FOUND ME,
NOBODY EVER LOOKED OUT FOR HIM.

25:45.277 --> 25:47.013
- ANYTHING MORE, MARTIN?

25:47.013 --> 25:49.348
- NO, PABLO, YOU GOT HOMEWORK
FOR TOMORROW, RIGHT?

25:49.348 --> 25:53.786
WELL, GET UPSTAIRS
AND GET GOING.

25:53.786 --> 25:56.889
I THOUGHT YOU GUYS WERE WORKING
ON THE JOHNNY DUBCEK CASE.

25:56.889 --> 26:00.727
- YEAH, THE BOYS, THEY BOTH
WENT TO SETTLEMENT HOUSE

26:00.727 --> 26:02.061
AND YOUR CAMP.

26:02.061 --> 26:03.730
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

26:03.730 --> 26:07.767
WHAT'S THAT GOT TO DO
WITH THE PRICE OF COFFEE?

26:07.767 --> 26:10.236
ARE YOU TRYING TO SAY
THIS CAMP HAD SOMETHING TO DO

26:10.236 --> 26:12.104
WITH THOSE BOYS' BEHAVIOR?

26:12.104 --> 26:15.207
- REGGIE RHODES TOLD DETECTIVES
THAT HE WAS RAPED

26:15.207 --> 26:17.610
HERE AT THIS CAMP,
THREE SUMMERS IN A ROW.

26:17.610 --> 26:20.379
- YEAH, THE GUY BASHES
SOMEONE'S HEAD IN.

26:20.379 --> 26:22.682
HE'S ABOUT TO GET
THE NEEDLE FOR IT.

26:22.682 --> 26:25.952
NATURALLY, HE'S GOING TO LOOK
FOR SOME WAY TO SAVE HIS HIDE.

26:25.952 --> 26:29.021
- MARTIN, NO ONE'S
SAYING IT WAS YOU,

26:29.021 --> 26:31.057
BUT YOU TOLD US,
ANY WHIFF OF TROUBLE,

26:31.057 --> 26:32.759
AND YOU'D KICK
THE COUNSELOR OUT.

26:32.759 --> 26:36.162
SO ANYTHING HAPPEN
WHILE REGGIE WAS HERE?

26:36.162 --> 26:39.165
- YOU WANT ME TO LIE?

26:39.165 --> 26:41.400
- IT'S PAST THE STATUTE
OF LIMITATIONS.

26:41.400 --> 26:46.038
SO THIS CAMP, YOU...

26:46.038 --> 26:49.275
YOU KNOW, WE COULD ENSURE
THERE'D BE NO LIABILITY.

26:55.247 --> 26:57.750
- GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE!

26:57.750 --> 27:00.687
I DON'T WANT THAT BOY UPSTAIRS
TO HEAR ANY OF THIS!

27:00.687 --> 27:01.788
GO ON!

27:01.788 --> 27:05.391
GET OUT!

27:17.069 --> 27:18.404
- MS. LATHROP, YOU WERE
THE ASSISTANT PROSECUTOR

27:18.404 --> 27:19.872
IN THE CASE
AGAINST REGGIE RHODES?

27:19.872 --> 27:21.307
- IT WAS MY FIRST MURDER TRIAL
AS LEAD COUNSEL.

27:21.307 --> 27:23.342
- SO YOU HAD A LOT
RIDING ON THIS CASE.

27:23.342 --> 27:25.912
- FRANKLY, IT WAS A GOOD ONE
TO CUT MY TEETH ON.

27:25.912 --> 27:27.446
AND I WAS SUPERVISED

27:27.446 --> 27:29.749
BY THE LEAD PROSECUTOR,
JIM HARRISON.

27:29.749 --> 27:31.818
YOU'RE PREPARING
RHODES'S CLEMENCY HEARING?

27:31.818 --> 27:34.453
- MM-HMM. AND WE FOUND
MITIGATING CIRCUMSTANCES

27:34.453 --> 27:36.388
THAT WE THINK THE JURY
SHOULD HAVE HEARD.

27:36.388 --> 27:38.290
- LIKE WHAT?
IT WAS OPEN AND SHUT.

27:38.290 --> 27:39.959
- WELL, FOR ONE,
THAT DANFORTH

27:39.959 --> 27:42.394
MAY HAVE BEEN PAYING RHODES
FOR SEX.

27:42.394 --> 27:43.429
- IS THAT WHAT
HE'S TELLING YOU NOW?

27:43.429 --> 27:45.097
EVERYBODY HAS A STORY.

27:45.097 --> 27:46.432
- WELL, WE THINK REGGIE
MIGHT HAVE BEEN ABUSED

27:46.432 --> 27:48.034
THE NIGHT
BEFORE HE KILLED DANFORTH.

27:48.034 --> 27:49.468
IF YOU HAVE ANY WAY
TO CORROBORATE THAT--

27:49.468 --> 27:51.103
- I DON'T.
- WELL, YOU DO KNOW

27:51.103 --> 27:53.940
THAT DANFORTH HAD A RECORD
FOR SOLICITATION.

27:53.940 --> 27:57.777
- THAT WAS PUBLIC INFORMATION.
- SO THE DEFENSE KNEW ABOUT IT?

27:57.777 --> 27:58.878
- OF COURSE.
I WAS PREPARED

27:58.878 --> 28:02.048
FOR HIM TO BRING IT UP.
HE NEVER DID.

28:04.216 --> 28:06.819
THERE ARE PEOPLE ON DEATH ROW
THAT DESERVE CLEMENCY,

28:06.819 --> 28:10.890
BUT REGGIE RHODES--
HE DESERVES TO DIE.

28:13.425 --> 28:15.227
- SHE SEEM
A BIT DEFENSIVE TO YOU?

28:15.227 --> 28:16.996
- I THINK
SHE WAS HELPFUL.

28:16.996 --> 28:18.798
SHE TOLD US THAT REGGIE'S LAWYER
KNEW DANFORTH HAD A RECORD

28:18.798 --> 28:20.266
AND DIDN'T USE IT.

28:20.266 --> 28:21.801
THAT SPEAKS OF NEGLIGENCE.

28:21.801 --> 28:25.171
- IS THAT ENOUGH?

28:28.274 --> 28:31.177
- THE FIRST SUMMER
REGGIE CAME HOME FROM CAMP,

28:31.177 --> 28:33.279
I WAS HELPING
WITH HIS LAUNDRY,

28:33.279 --> 28:37.483
AND HIS...

28:37.483 --> 28:39.118
[sighs]

28:39.118 --> 28:41.520
HIS UNDERWEAR
WAS STAINED WITH BLOOD.

28:41.520 --> 28:46.492
MAMA SAW IT,
AND SHE DIDN'T EVEN SAY A WORD.

28:46.492 --> 28:48.460
SHE JUST PUT IT
IN THE WASH.

28:48.460 --> 28:50.296
- AND WHEN WAS THIS?
- REGGIE WAS 13.

28:50.296 --> 28:52.765
I WAS 17,
HOME VISITING.

28:52.765 --> 28:54.000
- AND YOU WEREN'T LIVING
WITH YOUR MOTHER?

28:54.000 --> 28:57.303
- NOT AT THAT TIME.
I FELT SORRY FOR REGGIE.

28:57.303 --> 28:59.305
BUT MAMA WAS USING,

28:59.305 --> 29:01.874
AND I COULDN'T FIGHT HER
AND HER BOYFRIEND.

29:01.874 --> 29:04.977
- DID YOU TELL REGGIE'S
DEFENSE LAWYER ABOUT THIS?

29:04.977 --> 29:06.445
- YEAH, I CALLED HIM
OUTSIDE THE COURTHOUSE.

29:06.445 --> 29:09.448
AND BEFORE I COULD
GET TEN WORDS IN,

29:09.448 --> 29:12.484
HE TOLD ME
TO SHUT THE "F" UP,

29:12.484 --> 29:15.487
THAT THE JURY
DID NOT NEED TO KNOW

29:15.487 --> 29:17.489
THAT REGGIE WAS A HOMO.

29:17.489 --> 29:19.291
- THANK YOU, MS. SMITH.

29:19.291 --> 29:23.062
- MR. ELLIS, THIS HISTORY
OF ABUSE IS HORRIBLE.

29:23.062 --> 29:24.864
AND THE FACT THAT
MR. RHODES'S ORIGINAL COUNSELOR

29:24.864 --> 29:27.466
NEVER BROUGHT IT
TO THE ATTENTION OF THE JURY

29:27.466 --> 29:29.035
ONLY COMPOUNDS
THE NEGLIGENCE.

29:29.035 --> 29:30.302
- WELL, THANK YOU,
MS. BROOKS.

29:30.302 --> 29:32.338
HERE ARE
OUR SWORN AFFIDAVITS

29:32.338 --> 29:34.040
FROM SEVEN
OF THE ORIGINAL JURORS,

29:34.040 --> 29:36.175
STATING THAT,
HAD THEY KNOWN THIS HISTORY,

29:36.175 --> 29:39.211
THEY WOULD NOT HAVE SENTENCED
REGGIE RHODES TO DEATH.

29:39.211 --> 29:40.546
- EVEN THOUGH YOUR CLIENT
NOW ADMITS TO THE MURDER

29:40.546 --> 29:42.348
HE PREVIOUSLY DENIED?

29:42.348 --> 29:44.383
- OH, YES, THEY ALL AGREED THAT,
GIVEN THIS LEVEL

29:44.383 --> 29:45.852
OF DEFENSE NEGLIGENCE,
IT WOULD BE

29:45.852 --> 29:47.486
A GRAVE MISCARRIAGE
OF JUSTICE

29:47.486 --> 29:50.156
FOR THE STATE
TO EXECUTE REGGIE RHODES.

29:50.156 --> 29:53.325
- THANK YOU, COUNSELOR.
WE WILL RULE WITHIN 24 HOURS.

29:53.325 --> 29:56.162
THIS CONCLUDES
THE HEARING.

29:56.162 --> 29:57.830
- GOOD JOB, ELLIS.

29:57.830 --> 29:59.398
YOU BROUGHT UP ENOUGH
TO GET THE CASE RETRIED.

29:59.398 --> 30:01.167
- WELL, ONE STEP AT A TIME.

30:01.167 --> 30:03.602
LET'S JUST FOCUS
ON THE STAY OF EXECUTION.

30:03.602 --> 30:06.839
- WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

30:06.839 --> 30:09.876
- WE WAIT, REGGIE.

30:15.547 --> 30:18.517
- HEY, YOU'RE BOTH HERE.
THAT MUST MEAN GOOD NEWS.

30:18.517 --> 30:24.090
- THEY VOTED FIVE TO FOUR
AGAINST US.

30:24.090 --> 30:25.591
- I'M SORRY, REGGIE.

30:25.591 --> 30:28.360
- BUT I THOUGHT--
HOW DID THIS HAPPEN?

30:28.360 --> 30:29.528
- I DON'T KNOW, REGGIE,

30:29.528 --> 30:32.831
BUT WE'RE GONNA TRY
AND FIND OUT.

30:34.566 --> 30:37.870
- MM.

30:39.371 --> 30:42.074
- THE PAROLE BOARD
SAYS IN THEIR OWN DECISION

30:42.074 --> 30:44.911
THAT REGGIE'S DEFENSE WAS
UNCONSTITUTIONALLY DEFICIENT.

30:44.911 --> 30:47.146
THIS DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
- KEEP READING.

30:47.146 --> 30:49.648
- AND THEN THEY VOTE
FIVE TO FOUR,

30:49.648 --> 30:51.984
"THAT THE NEGLIGENT DEFENSE
DOESN'T RISE TO THE LEVEL

30:51.984 --> 30:55.087
OF INVALIDATING THE SANCTITY
OF A JURY'S DECISION."

30:55.087 --> 30:56.923
WHAT AM I MISSING?

30:56.923 --> 30:59.959
- FOUR VOTES.
NO OFFENSE, EX-COPS. C.O.s.

30:59.959 --> 31:03.395
- I SAW THEM ROLLING THEIR EYES
WHEN THE SISTER WAS TESTIFYING.

31:03.395 --> 31:06.933
BUT THE FIFTH VOTE,
THE CHAIR.

31:06.933 --> 31:08.367
SHE WAS ASKING
ALL THE RIGHT QUESTIONS.

31:08.367 --> 31:09.668
- OH, YES, SHE DID,

31:09.668 --> 31:12.204
WHICH MAKES IT HARDER
TO ACCUSE HER OF BIAS.

31:12.204 --> 31:13.572
- BIAS?

31:13.572 --> 31:15.975
SHE'S THE FORMER HEAD
OF SOCIAL SERVICES.

31:15.975 --> 31:17.944
- SHE ALSO SHOULD
HAVE RECUSED HERSELF.

31:17.944 --> 31:20.212
I GOT AN OFF-THE-RECORD CALL
THIS MORNING.

31:20.212 --> 31:23.382
MS. BROOKS IS MARRIED
TO JIM HARRISON.

31:25.484 --> 31:28.120
- THE LEAD PROSECUTOR

31:28.120 --> 31:30.222
WHO SUPERVISED
D.A. LATHROP

31:30.222 --> 31:35.327
AS SHE "CUT HER TEETH"
ON REGGIE'S TRIAL.

31:35.327 --> 31:39.165
OH, MY GOD.

31:39.165 --> 31:40.632
THIS WAS RIGGED.

31:40.632 --> 31:43.602
- IT'S BEEN RIGGED
AGAINST REGGIE FROM THE GET.

31:43.602 --> 31:45.171
- SO THAT'S IT?

31:45.171 --> 31:49.108
- NO, THERE MAY BE
JUST ONE LAST SHOT.

31:56.282 --> 31:58.184
- PROSECUTORIAL MISCONDUCT?

31:58.184 --> 32:01.387
PROSECUTORS MAKE MISTAKES,
CAN BE NEGLIGENT.

32:01.387 --> 32:03.322
BUT IN THIS CASE,
YOU'RE ALLEGING

32:03.322 --> 32:06.058
THAT THEY INTENTIONALLY
WITHHELD EVIDENCE?

32:06.058 --> 32:07.659
- YES, IF THE PROSECUTORS
KNEW ABOUT REGGIE'S ABUSE

32:07.659 --> 32:09.561
AND HID THAT
FROM THE DEFENSE,

32:09.561 --> 32:11.663
THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT WE'RE TALKING ABOUT HERE.

32:11.663 --> 32:13.365
- 20 YEARS,
AND IT'S NEVER COME OUT?

32:13.365 --> 32:15.534
RHODES IS SENTENCED
TO DIE IN FIVE DAYS.

32:15.534 --> 32:17.736
FORGIVE ME, COUNSELOR,

32:17.736 --> 32:20.672
BUT ISN'T THIS THE DEFINITION
OF A HAIL MARY?

32:20.672 --> 32:22.608
- AND AS THE PAROLE BOARD
JUST AFFIRMED,

32:22.608 --> 32:26.612
THE DEFENSE WAS
UNCONSTITUTIONALLY INCOMPETENT.

32:26.612 --> 32:28.580
- I WON'T GRANT
A STAY OF EXECUTION.

32:28.580 --> 32:30.482
YOU CAN HAVE THE FILES...

32:30.482 --> 32:32.551
TILL NOON TOMORROW.

32:32.551 --> 32:34.486
- YOUR HONOR, IT'S 5:00 P.M.
THAT'S LESS THAN 24 HOURS.

32:34.486 --> 32:37.556
- YOUR CLIENT
HAS HAD 20 YEARS.

32:37.556 --> 32:39.625
TAKE IT OR LEAVE IT.

32:39.625 --> 32:42.961
- YES.
THANK YOU, YOUR HONOR.

32:46.232 --> 32:47.766
- BAYARD, LOOK AT THIS.

32:47.766 --> 32:50.202
LOOK AT THIS.

32:50.202 --> 32:52.704
THESE ARE THE CRIME SCENE PHOTOS
THAT WERE SHOWN TO THE JURY.

32:52.704 --> 32:56.108
THESE I JUST FOUND.
THEY'RE WIDER SHOTS.

32:56.108 --> 33:00.612
LOOK AT THE BLOODY FOOTPRINTS,
AND LOOK AT THE BARE SPOT.

33:00.612 --> 33:03.082
IT'S MISSING
EVIDENCE SHADOWS.

33:03.082 --> 33:04.550
THEY SANITIZED
THE CRIME SCENE.

33:04.550 --> 33:07.153
- I'LL KEEP GOING,
YOU GO SEE IF REGGIE REMEMBERS

33:07.153 --> 33:09.588
WHAT WAS ON THE FLOOR.

33:09.588 --> 33:11.390
- YEAH,
DANFORTH TOOK PICTURES.

33:11.390 --> 33:13.525
THAT'S WHY I WENT BACK
THE NEXT DAY TO TELL HIM

33:13.525 --> 33:15.327
TO GIVE THEM BACK.

33:15.327 --> 33:18.497
- SO THE MEN TOOK POLAROIDS
THE NIGHT THEY WORKED YOU OVER?

33:18.497 --> 33:20.166
- YOU KNOW,
I HEARD CLICKS.

33:20.166 --> 33:22.168
I SEEN FLASHES.

33:22.168 --> 33:24.170
I SAID, "STOP IT."

33:24.170 --> 33:26.538
I SAID,
"NO MORE PICTURES."

33:26.538 --> 33:30.142
THEN I WENT BACK TO DANFORTH.
I TRIED TO GRAB THEM FROM HIM.

33:30.142 --> 33:31.643
THEY FELL
ALL OVER THE FLOOR.

33:31.643 --> 33:35.147
I LOOKED AT THE PICTURES,
AND I GOT SO MAD.

33:35.147 --> 33:39.485
I DON'T WANT ANYBODY
TAKING PICTURES OF ME.

33:39.485 --> 33:44.190
NOT ANYMORE.

33:44.190 --> 33:49.561
- REGGIE, DID SOMEBODY ELSE
TAKE PICTURES OF YOU?

33:49.561 --> 33:52.631
- [scoffs]
PICTURES AND MOVIES.

33:52.631 --> 33:56.302
THEY SAID THEY'D SHOW EVERYBODY
IF I TOLD.

33:56.302 --> 33:59.605
- IT WAS HUMILIATING.

33:59.605 --> 34:02.641
COACH SCHULTZ...

34:02.641 --> 34:05.511
VIDEOTAPED ME AND HIM
IN HIS BASEMENT.

34:05.511 --> 34:10.282
[sniffs] HE SAID IF I TOLD,
HE'D SHOW EVERYBODY.

34:13.785 --> 34:15.621
WHAT?

34:15.621 --> 34:20.226
- WELL, IT MIGHT EXPLAIN
WHY YOU WENT OFF ON COACH ALEXEI

34:20.226 --> 34:23.595
WHEN YOU SAW HIM
VIDEOTAPING THOSE BOYS.

34:25.297 --> 34:27.566
- I DON'T--
I DON'T WANT ANYONE TO KNOW.

34:27.566 --> 34:30.436
I DON'T WANT
ANYONE TO KNOW.

34:30.436 --> 34:33.272
- IF SCHULTZ TAPED JOHNNY,
EVEN IF HE LETS US USE IT,

34:33.272 --> 34:34.606
THE STATUTE'S RUN OUT.

34:34.606 --> 34:36.208
- BUT NOT ON POSSESSION
OF CHILD PORN.

34:36.208 --> 34:37.676
LOOK, SCHULTZ
REMEMBERED DETAILS,

34:37.676 --> 34:39.611
I MEAN,
WHAT THE BOYS WORE.

34:39.611 --> 34:41.180
IT'S LIKE HE'S BEEN REPLAYING
A HIGHLIGHT REEL.

34:41.180 --> 34:42.814
I BET HE STILL HAS
THOSE TAPES.

34:42.814 --> 34:44.516
- LET'S CALL THE D.A. AND GET
A WARRANT BEFORE HE STARTS

34:44.516 --> 34:46.552
TAPING THE KID
HE'S GOT UP THERE NOW.

34:46.552 --> 34:49.555
- WITH JUST THREE DAYS TO GO
BEFORE THE EXECUTION,

34:49.555 --> 34:52.424
ACTIVIST ATTORNEY BAYARD ELLIS
HAS FILED A MOTION

34:52.424 --> 34:55.327
ALLEGING
PROSECUTORIAL MISCONDUCT.

34:56.695 --> 35:01.533
- DAMN, LOOKS LIKE
HE GOT RID OF EVERYTHING.

35:01.533 --> 35:03.835
- DO YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE VIDEOS THAT WERE IN HERE?

35:03.835 --> 35:05.637
- COACH TOLD ME
NOT TO SAY.

35:05.637 --> 35:09.575
- PABLO, CAN I TALK
TO YOU FOR A SECOND?

35:09.575 --> 35:12.211
COME ON.

35:15.214 --> 35:17.183
- MS. LATHROP, REGGIE RHODES
WAS THE FIRST HOMICIDE

35:17.183 --> 35:18.884
YOU TRIED
AS A LEAD PROSECUTOR,

35:18.884 --> 35:20.652
AND IT WAS
A DEATH PENALTY CASE.

35:20.652 --> 35:22.521
SOUNDS LIKE
A LOT OF PRESSURE.

35:22.521 --> 35:24.756
- IT WAS A PARTICULARLY
BRUTAL MURDER.

35:24.756 --> 35:26.825
IT WAS MY DUTY TO SEE
THAT JUSTICE WAS DONE

35:26.825 --> 35:29.561
FOR THE VICTIM
AND FOR HIS FAMILY.

35:29.561 --> 35:31.563
- AND GIVEN THAT THE DEFENDANT'S
LIFE WAS AT STAKE,

35:31.563 --> 35:33.765
YOU OF COURSE
FAMILIARIZED YOURSELF

35:33.765 --> 35:35.634
WITH ALL ASPECTS
OF THIS CASE?

35:35.634 --> 35:37.503
- WELL,
I HAD A SUPERVISOR,

35:37.503 --> 35:38.704
BUT I LIVED WITH IT
EVERY DAY

35:38.704 --> 35:40.439
UNTIL I GOT
THAT CONVICTION.

35:40.439 --> 35:42.541
SO...[chuckles]
YES, COUNSELOR,

35:42.541 --> 35:45.611
I WOULD SAY THAT I KNOW
THE FACTS AS WELL AS ANYONE.

35:45.611 --> 35:47.479
AND THE LAW.

35:47.479 --> 35:49.848
- PLEASE DON'T TELL HIM
I SHOWED YOU THIS.

35:49.848 --> 35:52.318
- MARTIN ASKED YOU
TO BURN THESE?

35:52.318 --> 35:53.785
- THE DAY
AFTER YOU GUYS WERE HERE.

35:53.785 --> 35:55.687
HE HAD BOXES OF THEM.

35:55.687 --> 35:58.190
YOU KNOW,
OLD SPORTS TAPES.

35:58.190 --> 35:59.491
- BOXES.

35:59.491 --> 36:02.561
WELL, THAT WOULD
HAVE TAKEN A LONG TIME.

36:02.561 --> 36:06.198
- THE FIRE WENT OUT.
I DIDN'T GET TO THEM ALL.

36:07.566 --> 36:09.435
- AND I'M SURE YOU
THOROUGHLY INVESTIGATED

36:09.435 --> 36:11.603
BOTH THE VICTIM AND THE
DEFENDANT'S PERSONAL HISTORIES.

36:11.603 --> 36:13.772
- I'M A PROSECUTOR,
NOT A SOCIAL WORKER.

36:13.772 --> 36:15.441
BUT I DID MY JOB.

36:15.441 --> 36:17.709
- SO YOU WERE AWARE THAT,
AS A YOUNG BOY,

36:17.709 --> 36:20.912
REGGIE RHODES WAS SERIALLY
ABUSED BY A NUMBER OF ADULT MEN.

36:20.912 --> 36:22.881
- NEITHER HE NOR HIS DEFENSE
ATTORNEY BROUGHT THAT UP.

36:22.881 --> 36:24.750
- WELL, MS. LATHROP,
AT THE TRIAL, YOU TOLD THE JURY

36:24.750 --> 36:26.885
THAT THIS WAS A MURDER
BETWEEN STRANGERS.

36:26.885 --> 36:30.289
A ROBBERY GONE BAD,
CORRECT?

36:30.289 --> 36:31.923
- AND THE JURY AGREED
WITH ME.

36:31.923 --> 36:33.759
THEY HANDED DOWN
THE APPROPRIATE SENTENCE.

36:33.759 --> 36:35.394
- WERE YOU AWARE
OF A PRIOR RELATIONSHIP

36:35.394 --> 36:37.829
BETWEEN MR. RHODES
AND THE VICTIM?

36:37.829 --> 36:40.566
- I DON'T RECALL
EVER HEARING THAT.

36:40.566 --> 36:42.634
- AND YET DETECTIVES WERE ABLE
TO TRACK REGGIE RHODES DOWN

36:42.634 --> 36:44.870
BECAUSE THE VICTIM'S WIFE
I.D.'D HIM AS SOMEONE

36:44.870 --> 36:48.274
THE HUSBAND OFTEN HIRED
AS A HANDYMAN.

36:48.274 --> 36:51.410
- IT'S BEEN 20 YEARS,
BUT MY MEMORY

36:51.410 --> 36:54.546
IS THAT FORENSIC EVIDENCE
LED TO HIS BEING APPREHENDED.

36:54.546 --> 36:58.417
- FORENSIC EVIDENCE.
THAT WOULD INCLUDE FOOTPRINTS?

36:58.417 --> 37:00.819
- HEY. HEY!

37:00.819 --> 37:04.690
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU PEOPLE
DOING HERE, HUH?

37:04.690 --> 37:06.525
GET OFF MY PROPERTY!

37:06.525 --> 37:08.827
- GOT A WARRANT
TO SEARCH YOUR CRIB, COACH.

37:08.827 --> 37:13.899
- THIS IS FOR MY HOUSE!
YOU GOT NO BUSINESS IN MY SHED!

37:13.899 --> 37:15.567
THIS IS AN ILLEGAL SEARCH!

37:15.567 --> 37:17.603
